Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.91,0:00:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Princess Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,everypony at the\Nhospital is so excited
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,for your visit today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.37,0:00:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never too busy to visit\Nsick foals! I can't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole class just came\Ndown with the Horsey Hives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,... on school\Npicture day, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! The poor dears really\Ndo need cheering up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll bring snacks; I'll read\Nto them and get them gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Food and presents\Nalways cheer me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, if we want to be at\Nthe hospital by lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,then we have three hours\Nto buy get-well presents,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,borrow a book from\Nthe schoolhouse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.84,0:00:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and pick up treats.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lot, but if we\Nstick to the schedule,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we can get\Nit all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, knock on wood!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:00:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How's my\Nfavorite niece?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good! I was hoping\Nmy favorite aunt
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,could watch me for\Na few hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.56,0:01:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're\Nnot too busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.86,0:01:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, we kind of are--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Busy? Psh! Would the Best\NAunt Ever be "too busy"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to spend time with this\Nadorable little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.39,0:01:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles\NBy YayPonies\NCertified 100% without wife trowing!\Nhttps://yp1.yayponies.no
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Flur-ry, I've got\Na surprise for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a couple of toys that\Nreminded me of Flurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm excited to show you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done some shopping\Nfor Flurry Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so sweet. You\Ndidn't have to do all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but I\Ncan't help myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Best! Aunt! Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Open this one, Flurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! They're bears!\NYou're one smart cookie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just put Flurry's\Nthings over here, Twiley!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh huh, totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashed peas:\Nher favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And diapers, extra diapers,\Noh and backup extra diapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashed peas: her favorite.\NWait. Did I say that already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! And this is the most\Nimportant thing of all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Her "whammy".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I take it Flurry named it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. If she gets fussy,\Njust give her the whammy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and she'll calm\Nright down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You getting all\Nthis, Twiley?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Whammy! Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you guys\Nheaded anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember my friend from\Nthe royal guard, Spearhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, all of your friends'\Nnames are very similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he has a pop-up art\Nshow at the Ponyville Cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and we decided to go\Nat the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not exactly\Nart enthusiasts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but we could really\Nuse a night out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I said.\NIsn't that what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, are you\Nsure you can watch her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.78,0:04:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh uh uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Have no fear! The Best-Aunt-Ever\Nhas everything under control!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks again, Twiley!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, let's grab that\Nwharmmy thing and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, you wanna pretend\Nwe're the bears?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose we have\Ntime for a quick game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we though?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, rawr!\NI'm gonna getcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You should catch her soon\Ncause we've got lots to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Horsey-hive covered foals\Ncounting on us, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. Rawr, rawr!\NI'm catching up! Rawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,RAWWWWWR!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh. Sorry, bug.\NDid that scare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK! It's just\NAuntie Twiley!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that was a\Nvery advanced spell
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:05:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,for somepony your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're already taking\Nafter your Auntie Twiley!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that was pretty\Nadorable. But now--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, Spike. We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to feed\Nher real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this art...\Nor a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But who cares? We're\Nnot changing diapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shining Armor! Cadance!\NHow are the new 'rents?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me some hoof!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:07:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so! Good! To see you\Ndudes! Thanks for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! We're\Nhaving a great time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Loving all the art!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, that's a trash can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is. I knew that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But hey, who's to\Nsay it's not art?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Art can be anything\Nthat speaks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It changed my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my latest piece: A\NThousand Nights in a Hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I guess nighttime in a\Nhallway can be pretty dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There is none more dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just so happy to be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually we're covered\Nin mashed peas by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When they said mashed\Npeas were her favorite--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,--did they mean her favorite\Nthing to decorate a room with?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on, Spike.\NThat wasn't too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah and we're only twenty\Nminutes behind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty minutes? It's fine.\NWe can totally do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, we just need to grab some\Ntoys and we are out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Rawrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to play, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I know a game\Nthat's even more fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and more efficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing race cart! Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, nice thinking, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Best-Aunt-Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, Flurry. The race\Ncart's taking a pit-stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a detective, but\NI think we've got a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'd better\Nget to cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got no\Ntime to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but they were\Norganized by color.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! We gained back a whole\Nfive minutes from running here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but if you add\Nthat to the 40 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,we were already behind, we're\Nstill... 55 minutes behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... yay, team?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmhmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for helping us out,\NCheerilee! Sorry we were late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I gotta say, I'm\Nsurprised you came to me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,for a book. Don't you\Nhave a huge collection?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...\Nsorry, one second--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.99,0:10:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think the\Nfoals would be interested
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in The Unabridged History\Nof Amulets in Pony Latin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was good\Nyou came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the\Ncomplete collection
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of "Ponyville\NFables and Stables"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Alien Alicorns\Nvs. Space Pirates"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the science\Nthere is preposterous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Burnferno:\NWarrior from Within?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about a handsome dragon\Nwarrior who slays evildoers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,with his breath and\Nhis snappy comebacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:11:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's borrow that for you\Nand keep looking. What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How about "Gusty\Nthe Great"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! That was one\Nof my favorites
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was a filly!\NWe'll take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.93,0:11:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... should I go with\Nsomething more current?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Ta da! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheerilee! I am so, so sorry.\NI didn't even hear her leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There! All clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. Now I'll just write\Nit up again. With my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Feast your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's called 'A\NKitchen Guard's journey'.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This reminds me\Nof the time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Flurry got into the\Nchocolate pudding
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and we found little chocolate\Nhoofprints all over the carpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That took forever\Nto clean up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But remember how cute\Nher little face looked
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,when we caught her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah she was\Nlike... uh oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Art is\Nso evocative.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't even going\Nfor that memory! Score!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Twilight, I\Ndon't even want to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,how late we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I just cancel our\Nvisit to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Cancel? We\Ncan't cancel, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The sick foals are\Ncounting on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And the B.A.E. would never\Nthrow in the towel like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,B.A.E.?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Best-Aunt-Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, this errand is\Ngoing to be different!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you figure that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Flurry can play\Nwith the Cake twins
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and stay out of\Ntrouble! Best Aunt Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful, they're\Nfriends already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh! I shouldn't\Nhave doubted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Wait,\Nyou doubted me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, you watch Flurry; I'll\Ntake care of everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi Pinkie, how's it going? I\Nneed to pick up the cupcakes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,for the foals at the hospital\Nand can you do apology treats?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good. Here they\Nare. Of course I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still have a giant file\Nof everypony's favorite treat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In my secret party\Nplanning cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,BRB!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He he! Remind me to tell you\Nlater how amazing you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheerilee?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am pretty awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Cherry oatmeal cookies\Nwith yellow sprinkles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Can you write\N"sorry" on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a stamp for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys.\Nno need to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on! I'm sure\Nthere's another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, sweetie!\NWe'll play in a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The salespony at\Nthe toy store.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple strudel cupcake\Nwith caramel drizzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. You're making the\Nsame face Cheerilee made.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, remind me what\Nyour favorite treat is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The sampler platter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take\Nthree of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A-ha! told you I'd\Nfind another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the question! We\Nare NOT cancelling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be\NOK! It has to be OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so\Nterrible so far
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that it can't possibly\Nend up [splat]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I needed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just gonna\Nsay... we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're only\Nfour-and-a-half minutes late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Four-and-a-half?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"And while nopony had ever\Ntried to reach Cloudsdale
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,on hoof, Gusty the\NGreat was not deterred.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She and her unicorn warriors\Nmarched up the hill--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but suddenly they encountered--"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"It was the\Ntreacherous Grogar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And Gusty could tell he\Nwas ready for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:16:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Gusty called out to\Nthe unicorn warriors--"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,OW!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not right now, Flurry, these\Nfoals really want to hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"'We can fight\NGrogar... TOGETHER!'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And the unicorn warriors shot\Nmagical beams into the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that wove into one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The beam, stronger than a\Nthousand armies, shined down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It wrapped around Grogar and\Npulled him to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him escape!'\Nyelled Gusty!"--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Say aaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"Grogar was strong,\Nfor fear gave him power
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and he broke\Nthrough the bonds--"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! So good, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Look up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike! You're floating!\NYOU'RE FLOATING!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:16:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Flurry, honey, you\Nneed to stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Get us down, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony panic! Everything's\Ngoing to be OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I can't keep up with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! Where's her snoozal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Her what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You know her, whacky,\Nwompy-thing, the snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it? Cadance\Nsaid it calms her down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,FLURRY HEART! PUT US\NALL DOWN THIS INSTANT!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everypony OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Flurry that was\Nvery, very bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have\Nhurt somepony.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Flurry, I didn't mean to--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie, you don't have to be\Nscared; it's just me. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're scared of me.\NBecause I yelled at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a big scary bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Flurry, I'm so sorry. I've\Nbeen a terrible aunt today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All you wanted to do was play
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've barely been able to\Npay attention to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,None of this is your\Nfault. It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for being\Nthe Best Aunt Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hope you know\Nhow much I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I take it you forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Flurry. How\Nabout we head home?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,After we find your\Nwhammy, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This one kind of reminds\Nme of Flurry's hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one reminds\Nme of Flurry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's small, like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do this\Nanymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Spearhead, this has\Nbeen great but--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Say no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My art has always spoken\Nto me about what I love,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but knowing that it spoke\Nto you about what you love,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,speaks to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Flurry? Where's our\Nlittle foal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We missed you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks like you had\Na great time without us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, not so much. Flurry\Ngot into some mischief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't her fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have\Nagreed to watch her
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,with such a\Njam-packed schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was too much\Nto juggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But Flurry taught me an\Nimportant lesson today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.49,0:20:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It turns out being the\NBest Aunt Ever
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't about spending the\Nmost time with your niece,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but spending quality\Ntime with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And she taught me a\Nreally cool "bear" game,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so I guess I learned two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we definitely\Nshould have given you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,more of a head's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! From now on, we'll\Ngive you plenty of notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:20:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing\Nnext Tuesday?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For dinner! Not to babysit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to check with Spike,\Nbut I think we're free.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Spike, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"... the dashing dragon warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,breathed a scorching\Nflame from his snout
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then chuckled to himself\Nas he flew into the sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,'If you can't stand the heat,\Ndon't fight a dragon..'"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you kinda\Nlook like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Now who wants more cake?!
